 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The overall value of LVI-IPCC indicated that the vulnerability of farmers’ livelihoods to flood in the Sonorejo Village goes in the category of vulnerable or moderate by 0.044 on index figure. Although Jiwo Wetan has a lower LVI than Sonorejo, LVI Jiwo Wetan is still classified as vulnerable. LVI Score in Jiwo Wetan is −0.032. The agricultural insurance programme is proven to reduce losses for farmers in Jiwo Wetan. If the social network score in Sonorejo reaches 0.482, then in Jiwo Wetan it is at the level of 0.245.</p>
